WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:03.400
Chen Junnan, my brother, he didn't do it on purpose.

2
00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:05.000
Can you let him go?

3
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.866
So you came to me just to ask me to let your brother go

4
00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:09.733
As long as you let my brother go

5
00:00:09.733 --> 00:00:11.000
I can do whatever you want me to do.

6
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.933
Didn't you come to me because I was hurt?

7
00:00:12.933 --> 00:00:15.166
Am I so worthless in your heart?

8
00:00:15.666 --> 00:00:18.200
No, I just know

9
00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:20.533
Don't forget I can let your brother out

10
00:00:20.533 --> 00:00:22.066
We can put him back there.

11
00:00:22.133 --> 00:00:23.966
How can you let my brother go?

12
00:00:23.966 --> 00:00:25.300
You can let your brother go

13
00:00:25.300 --> 00:00:26.833
I want to know one thing.

14
00:00:27.666 --> 00:00:29.733
What kind of man do you like?

15
00:00:29.733 --> 00:00:30.800
Hmm what

16
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.733
I want to know what kind of man you like

17
00:00:32.733 --> 00:00:33.500
What do you like to eat?

18
00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:35.100
And what are your hobbies?

19
00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:36.500
I want to know everything

20
00:00:36.733 --> 00:00:38.066
I don't quite understand.

21
00:00:38.966 --> 00:00:40.133
The first step in chasing a girl

22
00:00:40.133 --> 00:00:41.833
Just to know what she likes

23
00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:43.966
You tell me now and I'll let you go right away

24
00:00:44.266 --> 00:00:45.700
I like to eat crayfish.

25
00:00:45.933 --> 00:00:48.033
Crayfish

26
00:00:48.166 --> 00:00:50.366
Hey, what are you doing to eat crayfish?

27
00:00:50.900 --> 00:00:52.966
You can't eat seafood with your current injury

28
00:00:52.966 --> 00:00:54.966
Then think about it, is there anything else?

29
00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:58.466
Others I can't think of right now

30
00:00:58.466 --> 00:01:00.600
I'll go to the bathroom first

31
00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:03.166
5 minutes go back 5 minutes

32
00:01:03.366 --> 00:01:04.500
Be gentle with girls

33
00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:06.500
Gentleness is the only magic weapon to chase a girl

34
00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:07.533
No more than 5 minutes

35
00:01:07.533 --> 00:01:09.633
You can go as long as you want. I'll wait for you.

